casebody.data:
ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION OF MARYLAND v. WALTER S. ORLINSKY [Misc. (BV) No. 21,

September Term, 1982.]

Order filed October 15, 1982.

Consent to disbarment filed by Walter S. Orlinsky in accordance with Maryland Rule BV12 d 2.

Walter S. Orlinsky is disbarred by consent from the further practice of law in the State of Maryland and his name stricken from the register of attorneys in this Court.
